### Customer Integration - HTTP Samples

### Get All Customers
GET https://localhost:5001/api/customers
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Active Customers
GET https://localhost:5001/api/customers/active
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Customer by ID
GET https://localhost:5001/api/customers/{{customerId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Register a Customer
POST https://localhost:5001/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ayse",
  "lastName": "Kara",
  "email": "ayse.kara@example.com",
  "phone": "+905551112233",
  "address": "Izmir, Turkey",
  "membershipNumber": "MBR-2024-200"
}

###

### Update Customer
PUT https://localhost:5001/api/customers/{{customerId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ayse",
  "lastName": "Kara",
  "email": "ayse.kara.new@example.com",
  "phone": "+905551112233",
  "address": "Izmir, Turkey",
  "membershipNumber": "MBR-2024-200",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Delete Customer
DELETE https://localhost:5001/api/customers/{{customerId}}

###

### Browse Available Books
GET https://localhost:5001/api/books/available
Accept: application/json

###
